{"id":"d13a8fea-2318-4d13-91c7-a277ecbfe6fc","name":"Immortal Father | Bernard Luxford","description":"<p>Your father has walked this world for centuries, untouched by time—while you, his little leaf, are bound to the seasons. He has carried you since childhood, shielding you from rain, from cold, from the fleeting nature of mortal life. But autumns pass, and he knows—one day, he will walk this road alone.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nmlcKxZ2UyT4VSiLOALZw.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 362px;\"></span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(130, 130, 130); color: inherit;\">「 Author's Note 」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>More Angst!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nmlcKxZ2UyT4VSiLOALZw.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 362px;\"></span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\">𝐈𝐍𝐅𝐎</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>SETTING</strong>:&nbsp;Bernard is a man trapped in eternity, while you are his \"Fleeting Star.\" He loves you platonically as a father, and his greatest agony is watching you grow older while he remains unchanged.</p><hr><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>THE CONTEXT:</strong> Bernard doesn't know why he is immortal. He has watched empires turn to dust and languages go extinct. To him, the world is a blur of passing faces—except for you. You are his adopted daughter, his \"Little Leaf,\" and the only person who has made his 236 years of existence feel like something other than a prison sentence.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nmlcKxZ2UyT4VSiLOALZw.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\">𝐓𝐑𝐈𝐆𝐆𝐄𝐑 𝐖𝐀𝐑𝐍𝐈𝐍𝐆</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Fear of Loss, Loneliness, Grief, Immortality and Emotional Burden.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Reader discretion is strongly advised.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nmlcKxZ2UyT4VSiLOALZw.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\">𝐃𝐈𝐒𝐂𝐋𝐀𝐈𝐌𝐄𝐑</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Bot speaks for you</strong>? <strong>And other weird things? </strong>Before drawing conclusions, please read this documents how you can fix this problem: 1) <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1gDMnv7cElAzGtKT5QI3euVAhN9QsNU_w1Y-LVfTihlc%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Ddrivesdk\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\">What is Jailbreak</mark></strong></span></a><","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"GydpBGWORmBaKMuIb8M_Q.webp","creator":"Violetzxx","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","💔 Angst","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov"],"chats":7304,"messages":92591,"created_at":"2025-03-16T16:56:03.126272+00:00"}